title: [1508521049] Prisoners Cook Haute Cuisine - Gordon Behind Bars
description:
The prisoners have one last chance to save the Bad Boys Bakery project, and cook some high class canapés for the Secretary of State for Justice in order to impress him, and secure some funding.

Subscribe for weekly cooking videos. 

If you liked this clip check out the rest of Gordon's channels:
